
** selfupdate

  - sudo port selfupdate

** install

  - sudo port install wget
  - sudo port uninstall wget
  - port search wget
  - port clean wget
  - port info wget

on usage 'install' afterwards the package is normally cleaned. use

  - $ find ~/build/cvs/darwinports/dports -name "*.o" 

for uncleaned packages.

** outdated

  - port outdated
  - port [-f] -u upgrade outdated

    -u uninstall non-active ports
    -f force mode
